405
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,230
Benarkah?

406
00:31:05,570 --> 00:31:08,440
Saya tiada memori indah
tentang tempat itu.

407
00:31:12,250 --> 00:31:14,250
Adakah awak tidak suka idea itu?

408
00:31:16,810 --> 00:31:18,110
Awak mahu ke mana?

409
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:20,900
Tidak, mari pergi ke sana.

410
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,330
Saya mahu pergi ke sana.

411
00:31:27,290 --> 00:31:28,490
Mari pergi.

412
00:31:35,870 --> 00:31:37,540
Ia sudah banyak berubah, bukan?

413
00:31:37,950 --> 00:31:39,150
Ya.

